<C>__{chief of police }
<D>__{wanna see something cool?}
<A>__{the chief inserts a finger into his nostril. then he fits his hand up there. soon his whole arm is up his nostril as he searches for something. john and peter are impressed. the chief grabs something and starts to pull. then out of his nose comes adrian, who fully forms as the shell of the chief's body slumps to the ground.}
<C>__{adrian}
