<D>__{but what about the cash? can we keep it or what?}
<C>__{adrian}
<D>__{sure, why not?}
<A>__{they high five. adrian smiles and waits. it is real hot down there. we hear a train coming in the distance. a fan circles slowly. they all wait for him.}
<C>__{lady}
<P>__{(mumbling to herself)}
<D>__{food stamps? they should call 'em "dude stamps." cause ever time i get one, some dude takes it away...}
